<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Supplementary description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Female genitalia</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
Tergite IX (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Betacixius sparsus Tsaur &amp; Hsu, 1991, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439753" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">8A, B, D</figureCitation>
) moderately sclerotized, with two nearly oval wax plates, separated from each other. Anal segment (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Betacixius sparsus Tsaur &amp; Hsu, 1991, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439753" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">8C</figureCitation>
) rectangular, widening to apex, 1.1 times wider than long in dorsal view, anal style strap-like. Gonapophysis VIII (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Betacixius sparsus Tsaur &amp; Hsu, 1991, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439753" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">8E</figureCitation>
) elongate, and slightly curved upwards. Gonapophysis IX (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Betacixius sparsus Tsaur &amp; Hsu, 1991, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439753" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">8F</figureCitation>
) with two middle teeth, distance ratio between distal middle tooth to apex and length of denticulate portion is 2.3. Gonoplac (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Betacixius sparsus Tsaur &amp; Hsu, 1991, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439753" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">8G</figureCitation>
) rod-like, 3.8 times longer than wide in lateral view. Posterior vagina pattern as shown in Figure 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Betacixius sparsus Tsaur &amp; Hsu, 1991, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439753" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">8H, I</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
